[English]

Log2 is a log system in Java very light and simple.
I wrote it because I needed verbose log for debug and simple to use.

There is no configuration by default, no threads, no caching, no configuration
classes, no jar to include.
I use it extensively, and I don't have any known bug in pending resolution.

The repository is an Eclipse project.

I added the implementation of org.slf4j.* to support this framework log.

